Title : Mark Hoppus production discography
Text : {{Use mdy dates|date=April 2014}}
[[File:MarkIntheHondaCivicTour.jpg|thumb|260px|right|Hoppus on the [[10th Annual Honda Civic Tour]] in 2011.]]
The following list is a '''discography of production by [[Mark Hoppus]]''', an American musician and record producer. It includes a list of guest appearances, songs produced, co-produced, written and remixed by year, artist, album and title. This does not include his work with [[Blink-182]], [[+44 (band)|+44]], and [[Nothing and Nobody]]. 

Hoppus has produced albums by bands such as [[Motion City Soundtrack]], [[New Found Glory]], [[Idiot Pilot]] and [[The Matches]].
==Production discography==
